<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<add>nehst</add>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Nikel Erharts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., also
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Burkart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Reikarczhof<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache zu
                        disem mal von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>,
                        daz ir in darinn <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn, im des
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und
                                <expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wol getrawen. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                                <expan>furstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
